wiki.content: “Si Antes Te Hubiera Conocido” is KAROL G’s new single, released on June 20, 2024 at the beginning of the summer season. The song features a theme deeply rooted in the merengue genre, which pays tribute to the Dominican Republic; in addition to showing tropical sounds and lyrics that explore longing and speculation about a love that could never happen, because the person in question is already engaged to someone else. The official video for the single offers a story that takes place in a tiki bar in the Dominican Republic, located near the beach. Here, KAROL G takes on the role of a waitress, where she is called to sing at the site’s karaoke, starting a festive spirit that ended up transforming into a gigantic fight with boys and girls of all kinds and conditions, showing the joyful and persevering spirit that characterizes Latinos.
